name: rsclone
description: RSClone provides information about films, television series, including frames, trailers, posters, wallpapers, as well as data on persons associated with film and television production: actors, directors, producers, screenwriters, cameramen, composers, artists and editors.
author: Uladzislau Kutarkin, Vera Krasnova, Pavel Priladyshev, Matsvei Dubaleka
